metadata.description: This 5:1 Edition MixTape Headz NFT is styled after the rap and hip-hop legend Snoop Dogg! It features a wardrobe inspired by Snoop Dogg's performance at Super Bowl LVI and tape label with his legendary "Drop It Like Its Hot" song. There will be no mistaken identity with this combination!
metadata.name: Snoop Dogg: "Drop It Like Its Hot" Edition
